name: JamCity
title: jQuery.JamCity
description: jQuery.JamCity uses the API from Last.Fm to get your Last.Fm account top albums (*Last.Fm api:* getTopAlbums), loved tracks (*Last.Fm api:* getLovedTracks), top tracks (*Last.Fm api:* getTopTracks), new releases (*Last.Fm api:* getNewReleases), or recent tracks (*Last.Fm api:* getRecentTracks). It then takes that information and displays a beautiful layout using CSS3, jQuery, etc. Enjoy showing off your music on your blog or website!
